---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Granite, Quartz, Marble & Tile in Ardmore, PA
description: Granite, quartz, marble, and tile — fabricated in-house on the Main Line since 2001, installed with a lifetime warranty, at wholesale pricing.
---

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero__copy">
    <span class="kicker">Ardmore · Since {{ site.since }}</span>
    <h1>Stone that makes the kitchen the heart of the house.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Granite, quartz, marble, and tile — fabricated in-house, installed with a lifetime warranty, and priced like a wholesaler because we are one.</p>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--dark" href="/contact/">Plan a Showroom Visit</a>
      <a class="btn btn--link" href="/contact/">Get a Free Estimate</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero__media">
    <img src="/assets/img/hero-kitchen.webp" alt="White shaker kitchen with quartz island, farmhouse sink, and pendant lighting" fetchpriority="high">
    <div class="hero__caption">Quartz island kitchen · Main Line install</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>The materials</h2>
    <a class="text-link" href="/countertops/">Browse all stone →</a>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid--4">
    {% for m in materials %}
      <a class="card" href="/countertops/">
        <div class="photo photo--tall"><img src="{{ m.image }}" alt="{{ m.alt }}" loading="lazy"></div>
        <span class="card__title">{{ m.name }}</span>
        <span class="card__meta">{{ m.desc }}</span>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<div class="band band--split">
  <div class="band__cell">
    <span class="kicker kicker--light">100+ five-star reviews</span>
    <p class="band__quote">&ldquo;Price-wise, these guys came in $3,000 less than Colonial. The owner himself came out to make sure the templating was done properly.&rdquo;</p>
    <span class="band__attr">Peter J. · Yelp · Google · HomeAdvisor</span>
  </div>
  <div class="band__cell band__cell--divided">
    <h3>See the slabs in person.</h3>
    <p class="band__note">Or shop at home — we bring samples and ideas to you.</p>
    <a class="btn btn--light" href="/contact/" style="align-self:flex-start">Get Directions</a>
  </div>
</div>
